# Sentinel-HFT Workstream 4 -- nightly RCA digest.
#
# Install via:
#   crontab -e
# and paste one of the lines below.
#
# The job runs daily at 05:30 local time, writes the digest to
# ${SENTINEL_DIGEST_DIR} (default ./out/digests), and archives both
# the rendered Markdown and the JSON sidecar.
#
# Backends (in priority order):
#   1. Anthropic API  -- export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY before running.
#   2. Template fallback -- always available; deterministic.
#
# Environment:
#   SENTINEL_HOME         project root (default: $HOME/Sentinel-HFT)
#   SENTINEL_ARTIFACTS    drill artifacts root (default: out/hl)
#   SENTINEL_DIGEST_DIR   digest archive (default: out/digests)
#   ANTHROPIC_API_KEY     optional; template backend if unset.
#
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Production entry (adjust SENTINEL_HOME):
# 30 5 * * * cd "$HOME/Sentinel-HFT" && \
#     /usr/bin/env python3 -m sentinel_hft.cli ai rca-nightly \
#         --artifacts "${SENTINEL_ARTIFACTS:-out/hl}" \
#         --digest-dir "${SENTINEL_DIGEST_DIR:-out/digests}" \
#         --backend auto \
#         --no-print \
#         >> var/log/rca_nightly.log 2>&1
#
# Smoke entry (template backend, no network, useful for dev):
# */15 * * * * cd "$HOME/Sentinel-HFT" && \
#     python3 -m sentinel_hft.cli ai rca-nightly \
#         --backend template --no-print >/dev/null 2>&1
